claim.claim-text:
1. An NBC warning light, comprising:
a plurality of warning indicators, comprising at least two light sources;
an electronics assembly operatively connected to selectively operate said warning indicators;
a switch, said switch having a plurality of operable positions, wherein each of said operable positions commands said electronics assembly;
a power source; and
wherein said warning indicators, said electronics assembly, said power source and at least part of said switch are contained within a case, said case having an upper section and a lower section, wherein said upper section is rotatable with respect to said lower section, and wherein said operable positions of said switch correspond to positions of said upper section with respect to said lower section, such that rotating said upper section with respect to said lower section actuates said switch into its operable positions respectively.
